title: fix dex limit for apis < 21
message:
fix dex limit for apis < 21

see: https://developer.android.com/studio/build/multidex.html
turns out that the dex format limits us to 64k references. by incorporating
both etheremj & zbar we were hoing ober that limit. apis >=21 (eg lolypop,
marshmellow, nougat) were fine just by setting multidex: true in build.gradle.
but pre api 21 (eg kitkat) require the modifications in this commit.

title: fix a race condition in camera_preview
message:
fix a race condition in camera_preview

if the user released the camera by pressing the back-key before the
camera_preview was created... well that would be bad. somehow this was
more likely to happen when we lined up a batch of toasts just before
starting the scan activity.
